{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act37side", "eventName": "追跡日落以西", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "GO-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "廢鐵與鉚釘", "storyInfo": "戰後由議會所支持的工人群體組建了倫蒂尼姆工業振興協會，費斯特作為顧問開始重啟科技研發以及協助城市重建。與此同時，資源短缺帶來的矛盾卻依舊存在。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g4_ordnancefactory", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>新奧克特里格區，小型載具廠</><p=2>1098年12月21日 6:13 P.M.</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊長，你們終於來啦！快幫我看看這張藍圖！奧克和我爭了半天，他說重新設計電能驅動分配閥完全是多此一舉。", "name": "熱情的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但按照我們的預測，未來一定會有越來越多的大型載具，從這座工廠送往倫蒂尼姆的每一個地塊！", "name": "熱情的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以就該未雨綢繆，提前做好準備。", "name": "熱情的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然等到真正使用這些載具的人發現載重和牽引力根本不夠，到時候肯定會回過頭來罵我們這群老東西保守——", "name": "熱情的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“這些人一點遠見都沒有！”這種話我可不想聽！", "name": "熱情的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別叫我隊長了。我們雖然關係不錯，但大家已經不是自救軍了。何況我們也都回到了自己的工廠。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，你覺得奧克真的沒想到這些嗎？他不過是想能省則省罷了。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我當然知道。但怎麼樣也不能給後輩留麻煩吧。", "name": "熱情的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "馬丁叔，我當然理解你的心情。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#12$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可這些事情還是得一步一步來嘛。可露希爾分享了不少她研究的無人機技術，我也想把這些新技術全部整合進我們的新型四足載具裡。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#12$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但電力供應、系統自動化，這些問題我們現在都還沒解決，光有藍圖沒用，還是得先立足現實慢慢推進啊。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#12$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "馬丁叔，先按奧克的方案，做個基礎版來解決燃眉之急。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的藍圖還是交給“倫蒂尼姆工業振興協會”存檔吧，別弄丟了。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在有議會支持，工業振興協會的目標就是在戰後重建維多利亞的技術實力，讓它重新站上國際領先地位，每一個新的想法都值得被重視。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正你是協會的顧問，最後怎麼定還是你說了算。", "name": "熱情的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，最近是不是大家提的新點子太多了……感覺快審不完了。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟大家難得能親眼看到自己的想法讓這座城市產生改變，當然會熱情高漲。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#12$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，工廠的生產線、貫穿所有街道的快速軌道系統，還有守護整座倫蒂尼姆的城牆和城防炮。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們完全能靠自己的雙手把它們打造成想像中的樣子。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸欸，費斯特，你說其他的我都贊成，但別是你“想像中的樣子”吧！我不想有天走在街上發現整條路被你改成遊樂園，大家都吊在滑索上飛來飛去！", "name": "熱情的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，那只是眾多提案裡唯一讓大家笑得特別開心的一個，不能代表我所有的創意吧……", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話說回來，你們工廠真的決定把奧克留在核心生產區嗎？我聽說他原本那間工廠跟你們的關係好像不太好。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每間工廠都有自己的技術機密，過去也因為搶訂單鬧得不太愉快，對吧……", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，這倒是。我們這邊也不是所有工人當年都加入了自救軍。", "name": "熱情的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過既然凱瑟琳已經說服其他工廠一起加入協會共享技術，我們這邊也沒什麼理由再藏著——", "name": "熱情的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人嗎！快來幫忙！", "name": "焦急的工人"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "馬修先生被人打了！", "name": "焦急的工人"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "55_g6_dusklentiavenue", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……先生，我們以前見過嗎？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，算不上，議長閣下。", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我叫馬修，只是個經營小工廠的商人。但最近的日子讓我不得不來向您抱怨幾句。", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以寫信給議會或者直接向工業振興協會求助。我現在……有別的事情需要仔細想想。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閣下，我聯合了十幾家停工的工廠寫了一封信給議會，可它已經被您擱置了快半個月了。", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "部分工廠停工是議會通過的決議。你應該比誰都清楚，倫蒂尼姆現在的物流港口是什麼情況吧？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是一家工廠的倒閉，可能會讓薩迪恩區或海布里區的幾百個家庭活不下去。", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是想為自己爭取一點空間——哪怕是私下談的都行。", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在這些停工的工廠，工人們連從黑市買藥的錢都湊不出來。那些在生產線上辛苦一輩子的老師傅可是比十台機器還值錢。", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信我的工人們，他們還能為這座城市做更多事情。", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是現在療養院裡那些珍貴的礦石病抑制劑卻全分給了那些早已沒救的傷兵。", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你到底想說什麼！", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#10$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是想幫您算一筆“經濟帳”——", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*維多利亞粗口*！", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#10$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punchsp4", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.5, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜反應過來的時候，拳頭已經砸在了對方的鼻樑上。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那名叫馬修的男人摀著流血的鼻子，另一隻手在口袋裡翻找手帕。"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "止不住的鮮血從指縫間滲出，把衣襟染得通紅。"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "周圍的人越聚越多，所有目光都直勾勾地盯著維娜。"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不是敵意，也不是憤怒，而是一種無聲的提醒——提醒著維娜的無力，提醒著她這一拳的可笑與無意義。"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#10$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我——", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閣下，我知道你為什麼生氣。我明白……但總要有人把這些話說出口。", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對我來說，說這些話也不好受。", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也曾是自救軍的一員，當初選擇留下來守住這座城市，而你是跟著那名卡特斯女孩一起來的。後來，你們離開了。", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等到典範軍進城後，我從凱瑟琳女士那裡得知你是他們的領袖。我沒有半點猶豫就同意工廠升起蒸汽迎接你們。", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是當我第一次穿著國王的衣服站在街上，代表議會向大家承諾美好未來的那個人時，卻沒有認出來是你。", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你明明知道有些承諾根本無法兌現。你救下一些人的同時也在犧牲另一些人，不是嗎？", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 0.8, "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想要讓男人閉嘴。"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她一把抓起男人的衣領，輕而易舉地把他拎了起來。可就在那一瞬間，她看到了他的眼睛，也看到了圍觀人群的眼睛。"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“推進之王總能用拳頭解決問題。”"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她多希望，這次也一樣。只要她再狠狠地砸下去，事情就能像過去那樣被輕鬆地解決。"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$aluminum", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一陣清脆的金屬撞擊聲，她口袋裡的東西掉了出來滾落在地。她已經很久沒吃過糖了，甚至忘了這盒糖果一直放在這件衣服裡。"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當初我們同意停工讓出源石燃料的時候，我們都相信過你。可現在我們只希望被犧牲的，不是自己。", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拳頭不是萬能的……“推進之王”。", "name": "憂傷的人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cnstrctnck", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……維娜！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請放開馬修先生。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "55_g8_siegeoffice", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>議長辦公室</><p=2>1098年12月21日 7:32 P.M.</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……還有，剛才馬修先生的話不能代表所有工人。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，我的話也不能。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只知道幾個夥伴透過我的關係搭上了羅德島，希望改善療養院的醫療設備。我們沒辦法變出更多設備，但至少能讓現有的資源發揮更大的作用。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我想大多數工人還是全心全意支持目前的醫療系統。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，費斯特，這不該由你來解釋，衝動的是我。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們已經做到了極限，能做的事都做了。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫療設備不斷改善，快速通行隧道重新啟用，統一供暖系統也在試驗中……這座城市在短時間內發生的變化已經幫助了很多人。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也多虧了你在議會裡幫我們擋下不少麻煩，還開了不少綠燈。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這本來就是我的職責。對了，凱瑟琳女士還好嗎？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奶奶？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……以她的性格，就算有事她也不會說。她連咳嗽都怕被別人發現。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除此之外，她還是跟以前一樣，雖然不用再親自下工廠，但還是忙得不可開交。我很少能見到她。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上個月我和她也有過一次類似的對話。凱瑟琳女士就坐在這張椅子上，我邀請她加入議會，但她拒絕了我。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有你們戰爭期間瞞過薩卡茲監視的秘密工廠以及藏在裡面的那件武器——", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……現在的倫蒂尼姆已經用不上它了。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確，這點我和凱瑟琳女士已經達成共識。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要你和凱瑟琳女士還能團結大部分工人，由你們自行保管那件武器也未必是件壞事。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "議會需要被監督，我也是。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今的議會還沒什麼成熟的制度，大多數人都還在摸索，也總有人想藉著議會的手來達成自己的目的。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但遲早他們會明白，過去那個圍繞著國王運作的議會早就不存在了。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是從國王被——呃——", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……國王被吊死的時候議會並沒有發生什麼變化，說到底不過是掌權者從國王變成了幾位公爵罷了。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到最近，皇家科學院僅存的那些院士才終於有機會重新整理、補完他們當年被迫中斷的《倫蒂尼姆城市志》研究。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整整上百萬字，院士們用了半輩子的時間修訂、完善，裡面涉及了倫蒂尼姆的各方面。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從沒想過自己有一天會透過這樣的角度重新認識自己的家鄉。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是從那些報告裡，我才第一次意識到其實這座城市早就開始反抗了……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“薩卡茲掌控倫蒂尼姆後，真正維持城市運轉的是那些還留在城裡的倫蒂尼姆人。他們不分身分、不論地位，自發地維持了大部分城市的基礎機能。”", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "院士們在報告裡把這場反抗視為我們現在這個新議會的雛形。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……聽起來有點……呃，強硬？不過仔細想想也滿有道理的。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我看到的不是這個，費斯特。戰爭期間，為了活下去我們的確可以暫時拋開所有私心和分歧……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可現在，我不確定了。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至連我自己都沒辦法保證每一次決策都能保持理性。我需要有人能拉住我，在我——", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你希望是我們？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我和凱瑟琳女士的約定。況且這把劍不就是你們鍛造好後親手交給我的嗎？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場戰爭摧毀了太多東西，如果倫蒂尼姆不想在這場時代變革中被拋下，還需要你們的幫忙。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然有時你們那些天才的點子會讓議會和科學院負責審核的人頭疼不已，但這不見得是壞事。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#4$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們自己的城防系統、被維多利亞公爵們忽視已久的自動化技術，還有蒸汽騎士時代結束後的全新威懾武器……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一樣都需要你們的協助。而這些必須是為了倫蒂尼姆，而不是為了某個特定的人。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特，我不值得你們的信任。現在的議會也還遠遠不值得……如果你有機會去看看馬修先生，請再替我向他道個歉。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會繼續在議會爭取能改善工人處境的政策。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "向大公爵採購的藥品已經在運送途中，只要能確保貨運管道的安全，情況很快就能緩解。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，有誰敢動公爵們的運輸艦？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#3$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我會繼續和公爵們安插在城裡的代表溝通。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果有我們能幫上忙的地方，隨時找我們。大家都在。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特從桌邊站起來，猶豫了一下卻沒有立刻離開。"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奶奶總是說我這個人太愛胡思亂想。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可那天當我第一次從工業振興協會帶回一堆大家為未來提出的方案時，她一句話都沒說。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒過多久，她就以身體狀況不佳為由從生產線上退了下來。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……維娜，我們其實都不討厭去想像未來。我們會撐過去的。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "辦公室裡變得安靜下來。維娜看著桌上堆積如山的文件，沉默了許久，伸手打開收音機。"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_button", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "滋滋——", "name": "廣播聲"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……就在今天傍晚，多位市民目睹了亞歷山德莉娜·維多利亞議長閣下親手懲治小人的一幕。", "name": "廣播聲"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "據稱，一名“紳士”試圖向議長行賄，企圖為自己謀取私利，而議長本人則以最直接的方式拒絕了對方。", "name": "廣播聲"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "越來越多市民認為，維多利亞議長閣下擁有足夠的人格魅力，足以——", "name": "廣播聲"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_button", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g7_subway", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>倫蒂尼姆地下</><p=2>1098年12月21日 8:01 P.M.</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4162_cathy_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來我們之間總算是建立起了一點信任。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_4162_cathy_1#9$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4162_cathy_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管是因為你們終於相信這條運輸線可以由一個人單獨押送……還是像你說的，大部分人真的已經離開了維多利亞。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_4162_cathy_1#8$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你還是帶著你的小機器，沒看出來你對我有多信任。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4162_cathy_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城裡到處都是走投無路的難民，我總得確保這批物資不會被人搶走。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_4162_cathy_1#9$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，我可沒說過你們不是威脅的一部分。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_4162_cathy_1#9$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過在倫蒂尼姆還真沒有多少人知道整合運動過去的凶名。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#8$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你清點一下吧，交易清單上的物資都在這裡。下一批藥品我也會準時送到。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4162_cathy_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說，你們大部分人都確實離開了，那位九……？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_4162_cathy_1#9$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她走了，或者說，她帶著那些在這座城市裡已經找不到家的同伴一起離開了。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#3$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，這不影響我們在城外的工廠繼續運作。你幫我們找的運輸線也還能繼續派上用場。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4162_cathy_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不跟著他們走嗎？現在的倫蒂尼姆，對感染者可不算什麼好地方。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_4162_cathy_1#4$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“不算什麼好地方”……還真是倫蒂尼姆人會用的委婉說法。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小時候，我確實好奇過故事書裡的倫蒂尼姆——住著國王和小公主的皇宮花園，還有像迷宮一樣適合探險的工廠。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#8$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可後來我明白了，倫蒂尼姆和維多利亞的其他地方沒什麼不同，哪裡都不適合安身立命。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#8$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒走只是因為總得有人留下來，而我更習慣腳踏實地地做點事。況且，現在的倫蒂尼姆對感染者的態度……其實還不算太差。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#3$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4162_cathy_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_4162_cathy_1#9$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我跟著他們只是因為他們救了我的命。但我可不像某些同伴，早就準備好赴死，還想好要如何死得其所。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……更何況最後他們的死往往還不值得。沒有人是該死的。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4162_cathy_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也救了不少人，這點，我得替工人們謝謝你。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_4162_cathy_1#10$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下次在城裡發傳單的時候記得順道來海布里區坐坐。你那身偽裝，我一眼就認得出來。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_4162_cathy_1#10$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#6$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4162_cathy_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貨物我清點完了，沒問題。我就帶著這些回去了。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_4162_cathy_1#10$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，凱瑟琳奶奶……", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#6$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4162_cathy_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說吧。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_4162_cathy_1#10$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……如果你身上那些長出石頭的地方半夜會痛，我知道幾個能讓自己好過點的小訣竅。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#6$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該很清楚我們能製造出來的藥……效果遠遠比不上那些專業藥廠的產品。", "name": "珀茜瓦爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#6$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4162_cathy_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，這些藥能騙過大部分工人，卻騙不了我自己。現在倫蒂尼姆流通的抑制藥幾乎都是這種貨色。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_4162_cathy_1#10$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但以我這個年紀能保持清醒的日子本來就不多了，熬過的苦日子也算不少。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_4162_cathy_1#10$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4162_cathy_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多清醒一天，多做一件該做的事，這樣就夠了。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_4162_cathy_1#11$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g7_subway", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們派去的人已經追查到整合運動在城外的據點，還有他們的兩家主要工廠和運輸管道。", "name": "維多利亞士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要封鎖這條通道嗎？", "name": "維多利亞士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用。就目前掌握的情報來看，他們對倫蒂尼姆的市民沒有直接威脅。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜提過，她對整合運動保持警惕有一部分是個人的原因。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她也承認當時整合運動鼓動倫蒂尼姆市民反抗公爵的行動，確實幫了我們一個大忙。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於現在這些灰色交易……只要確保它們還在我們的掌控之內就沒問題。珀茜瓦爾不是傻子，她知道什麼該碰，什麼不該碰。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整合運動的核心成員撤離倫蒂尼姆後，他們的威脅已經不高了，繼續監視他們就好。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至，如果我們的目標都是為了改善感染者的處境，那麼我們也不介意和他們有私下的接觸。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收到，我們會保持對整合運動的低強度監視。", "name": "維多利亞士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，這樣的工作對你們而言是大材小用。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——當然不會，戴菲恩閣下！", "name": "維多利亞士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從我們離開溫德米爾公爵的軍艦開始，到接近倫蒂尼姆時停止情報活動、專注突入戰場，再到現在……", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你會想念麗茵卡登的湖水嗎？", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#11$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}